<mxfile host="Electron">
  <diagram name="Page-1" id="FptqVHqOm2Rn9Q4Bc9s3">
    <mxGraphModel dx="4230" dy="2247" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="12000" pageHeight="16000" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="-PzeinkgOGFrqP16TIsL-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Aim: To design Google Docs" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="500" x="610" y="150" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="-PzeinkgOGFrqP16TIsL-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Functional Requirements:&lt;div&gt;1. User should be able to registration and login.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. User should be able access and edit documents aka perform CRUD&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;3. User should be able to collabrate in real-time on these specific documents&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;4. User should be able to handout permissions or restricts users from modifying specific documents if they don&#39;t have permission&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;5. User should be able to see the previous documents and their versions and revert back to past ones. Permissions can include editor,viewer and owner.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Non-Functional Requirements:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. Documents edit should be visible quicky withing 300ms aka low latency&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. CAP Theoram: Availabilty&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt; consistancy ?? because we want our system to record the changes and be available as if multiple are editing together it will very hard to maintain consistency. So, we go with eventual consistency&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. System should be durable no edits should be lost even if the system crashes&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. It should be scalable as well because we want to support millions of documents and handle very large no. of users&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;5. Users should be able to go back to the previous document state after leaving and coming back.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Core Entities:&lt;br&gt;1. users&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. documents&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. document content&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. operations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. version&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6. permission.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Api-Design&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;users:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. POST /auth/login&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;POST /auth/register&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;document:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;POST /documents&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;GET /documents/{doc_id}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;GET /documents/{doc_id}/content&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;permissions:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;POST /documents/{doc_id}/permissions&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;versions:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;POST /documents/{doc_id}/versions/{version}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. POST /documents/{doc_id}/versions/{version_id}/restore&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;notifications:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;POST /notifications/send&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;GET /notifications&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;export:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;POST /api/export{u can all specify the types word and pdf extra}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;POST /api/import{types handled by the service}&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="750" width="580" x="610" y="190" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
